# StringSegment Inequality operator

Compares two string segments for inequality.

```csharp
public static bool operator !=(StringSegment segA, StringSegment segB)
```

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| segA | The first string segment. |
| segB | The second string segment. |

## Return Value

`true` if the segments are not equal; false otherwise.
